snippet.title: Timesplitters 4 (2008) PS3 build footage
snippet.description:
a brief look at the recently dumped Timesplitters 4 tech demo, running on real hardware.

some things of note.
the build includes an "xenon" folder, likely meaning it was also compiled on Xbox 360. though the executable file for this is not included.
yes, those are Future Perfect UI elements taken from the Gamecube version. none of the menu options actually work though, either freezing on a load screen or (in the case of "challenges") displaying an actual error message.
